 "remarks": "Discover resort-style living at the desirable Rowayton Woods Complex. This spacious, turn-key, ground-level condo offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Inside you&apos;ll find new flooring and fresh paint, highlighting the open floor plan. The updated kitchen showcasing beautiful quartz countertops is ideal for entertaining guests. Enjoy tranquility on your serene, fully private/secluded outdoor patio with direct access to the lawn. Beyond your door, the complex features phenomenal amenities, including an inground pool, tennis courts, a beautiful lake, and walking trails for year-round enjoyment. The location is unparalleled: you&apos;re just about 1 mile from Rowayton Village and under 2 miles from the convenient shopping options on Connecticut Avenue.   NOTE: Unit is located on the ground level, requiring one flight of stairs down to access, the unit itself is a ranch.   Making this unit even more enticing is that the current owner will take care of the reaming balance of the HOA assessment prior to closing!",
